pdf.declaration.declaration.1 = I declare that this information correct and complete to the best of my knowledge.
pdf.declaration.declaration.2 = I am the child’s biological father or the mother’s spouse, civil partner or a partner (including same sex partners) who lives with the mother and child in an enduring family relationship.
pdf.declaration.declaration.3 = I will have responsibility for caring for the child.
pdf.declaration.declaration.4 = I will take time off to support the mother and/or care for the child.
